user_prompt_template.en:
source_lang={source_lang}
target_lang={target_lang}
document_title={document_title}
source_url={source_url}
learning_mode={learning_mode}
difficulty={difficulty}
cloze_max_sentences={cloze_max_sentences}
cloze_min_chars={cloze_min_chars}
cloze_max_per_chunk={cloze_max_per_chunk}

You will receive one or more chunks in this format:
chunk_id=chunk_0001_xxxxxx
chunk_text=\n<chunk text>

Return a JSON array. Each item MUST include:
{
  "chunk_id": "matching chunk id",
  "text": "cloze sentence(s)",
  "original": "plain text without cloze markers/html",
  "target_phrases": ["phrase 1", "phrase 2"],
  "note_hint": "optional hint"
}

Optional debug fields are allowed:
- "selection_reason": short reason why this candidate is selected
- "phrase_types": array of labels
- "learning_value_score": numeric score

Global requirements:
1) text must contain at least one cloze: {{cN::<b>PHRASE</b>}}(hint).
2) cN index increases by appearance order in each text.
3) original must not contain cloze markers or html.
4) use <b>...</b> for emphasis, do NOT use markdown **.
5) omit candidates shorter than cloze_min_chars or exceeding cloze_max_sentences.
6) if no suitable candidate exists, return an empty array.

Material profile: transcript_dialogue.
Intermediate rubric:
- Prefer idiomatic spoken collocations and discourse markers with transferable value.
- Usually 1-2 clozes per candidate.
- Preserve enough context to understand pragmatic intent.
- Avoid over-fragmented snippets.

chunk_text:
{chunk_text}

user_prompt_template.zh:
source_lang={source_lang}
target_lang={target_lang}
document_title={document_title}
source_url={source_url}
learning_mode={learning_mode}
difficulty={difficulty}
cloze_max_sentences={cloze_max_sentences}
cloze_min_chars={cloze_min_chars}
cloze_max_per_chunk={cloze_max_per_chunk}

你将收到一个或多个 chunk，格式如下：
chunk_id=chunk_0001_xxxxxx
chunk_text=\n<chunk 原文>

请返回 JSON 数组。每个元素必须包含：
{
  "chunk_id": "对应的 chunk id",
  "text": "包含 cloze 的句子",
  "original": "不含 cloze 标记或 html 的纯文本",
  "target_phrases": ["短语1", "短语2"],
  "note_hint": "可选提示"
}

允许附加调试字段：
- "selection_reason": 该候选被选中的简短理由
- "phrase_types": 标签数组
- "learning_value_score": 数值评分

全局要求：
1) text 必须至少包含一个 cloze：{{cN::<b>短语</b>}}(提示)。
2) 同一条 text 内 cN 按出现顺序递增。
3) original 不得包含 cloze 标记或 html。
4) 可以使用 <b>...</b> 强调，不要使用 markdown **。
5) 丢弃长度小于 cloze_min_chars 或句子数超过 cloze_max_sentences 的候选。
6) 若没有合适内容，返回空数组。

材料类型：transcript_dialogue。
难度规范（intermediate）：
- 优先可迁移的口语搭配和 discourse marker。
- 通常每条 1-2 个 cloze。
- 保留足够上下文以理解语用意图。
- 避免过度碎片化片段。

